### Patterns

Pattern | Description
------- | -----------
`([^/]+)` | Matched with any but `/`
`(\d+)` | Matched with any positive numbers.
`((?:\d*\.)?\d+)` | Matched with any positive numbers and floats.
`(.+)` | Matched with any and `/`
`(foo|bar|baz\|qux)` | Matched with `foo`, `bar` and `baz|qux`
`(foo|bar|\d+)` | Matched with `foo`, `bar` and any positive numbers.